description:
&lt;p&gt;The South West Region is looking for an empowered, resourceful and quick-thinking Emergency Preparedness, Resilience and Response Manager to join the team on fixed term secondment until 31st March 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will directly support local systems across the South West Region as well as working with colleagues internally to enhance and develop the level of emergency preparedness, resilience and response of the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate’s responsibilities will include the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Representing the South West Region at key stakeholder engagements including Local Resilience Forums.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting NHS provider and commissioner organisations in the preparation for and response to major, critical and business continuity incidents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading or supporting on regional EPRR technical projects, including consultations with external and internal stakeholders, and supporting local systems in translating guidance to operational planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is desirable that candidates have a strong working knowledge of the Civil Contingencies Act 2004, the NHS EPRR Framework 2015 and associated guidance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further details can be found in the attached Job Description &amp; Person Specificaiton document.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NHS England and NHS Improvement are currently working remotely due to COVID-19. Should the postholder be required to be attend an office, locations include: Taunton, Chippenham, Bristol, Gloucester, Saltash.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that the reason for the fixed term of this contract is to cover an internal secondment of the substantive post-holder.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employees of NHS England and NHS Improvement will find this vacancy listed on the Internal Expression of Interest site and should apply there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Alex Thompson&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Head of Emergency Preparedness, Resilience and Response&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address:alexander.thompson4@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
