&lt;p&gt;Name: Leigh Clarke&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Head of Emergency Preparedness, Resilience and Response&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: leigh.clarke2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
